<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    Contract Termination Request Received
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    We have received a request to terminate your mortgage contract. Our team will review this request and process it according to our policies.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>Termination Request Details:</strong>
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Contract Number:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{contractNumber}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Property:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{propertyName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Request Type:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{terminationType}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Request Date:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{requestDate}}</td>
    </tr>
</table>

{{#if reason}}
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:15px 0;">
    <strong>Reason Provided:</strong><br/>
    {{reason}}
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>What happens next:</strong>
</p>
<ol style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; padding-left:20px;">
    <li>Our team will review your termination request</li>
    <li>You will receive an email with the decision</li>
    <li>If approved, we will process any applicable refunds</li>
</ol>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    If you did not request this termination, please contact our support team immediately.
</p>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
    style="color:#ffffff; padding:8px 20px; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; font-family:Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:12px; display:inline-block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #049DC8 0%, #0082B5 100%); border: none; margin-top:15px;">
    View Request Status
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; margin-top:30px;">
    Best, <br />
    The {{projectName}} Team.
</p>
